   191	    - PARAM field builder returns a StructField with leaf order exactly
   192	      value/integer, value/float, value/string, value/boolean, accession, name, unit.
   193	    - PARAM round-trip with nullables: a row whose Accession, Unit, and String are all null reads back
   194	      as null on those three leaves while the populated row reads back its values.
   195	    - Written file reports ZSTD compression on read-back (PQ-02 internal-codec assertion).
