ThermoRawFileParser/README.md:87:                               indexed mzML if no format is specified.
ThermoRawFileParser/README.md:88:  -m, --metadata=VALUE       The metadata output format: 0 for JSON, 1 for TXT,
ThermoRawFileParser/README.md:137:Output file extension is determined by the used output format and (optional) gzip compression, for example, if format is MGF without gzip compression, the output file will receive `.mgf` extension, if format is mzML with gzip compression the output file will have `.mzML.gz` extension. All user input will be standardized to fulfill abovementioned requirements.
ThermoRawFileParser/README.md:142:Enables the retrieval spectra by (a) scan number(s) in [PROXI format](https://github.com/HUPO-PSI/proxi-schemas).

